{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Build a Tentree-style Shopify homepage.
    
    ### HERO
    • Full-width minimal hero with light parallax.
    • H1: “Premium Wall Art & Professional UV Printing Services”
    • Subheading: “Shop premium wall art or book same-day UV printing services.”
    • Two CTAs: Shop By Category → #wallart-tabs , Book Services → #service-tabs
    
    ### SILO 1 — WALL ART
    • H2 with ID="wallart-tabs": “Paintings & Posters by Category”
    • Below H2 create Tentree-style horizontal TABS (like Women | Men | Accessories):
       – Canvas Paintings (/collections/canvas-paintings)
       – Metal Posters (/collections/metal-posters)
       – Acrylic Posters (/collections/acrylic-posters)
       – UV Printed Frames (/collections/uv-printed-frames)
    • Under tabs show a horizontal scroll row of items (banners or featured products) that switch when tabs change. Match the Tentree “New Arrivals” layout: clean, minimal, large spacing, swipeable on mobile.
    
    ### SILO 2 — PRINTING SERVICES
    • H2 with ID="service-tabs": “Printing Services by Category”
    • Create Tentree-style tabs:
       – UV Flatbed Printing (/collections/uv-flatbed-printing)
       – Eco-Solvent Printing (/collections/eco-solvent-printing)
       – Latex Printing (/collections/latex-printing)
       – Signage Printing (/collections/signage-printing)
    • Each tab shows a horizontal scroll section of service banners/cards, same style as above.
    
    ### STYLE
    • Only one H1 on page.
    • Tabs must visually match Tentree: centered text, underline active tab, smooth fade/slide.
    • Aesthetic: minimal, clean, modern, rounded edges, soft shadows, airy spacing.
    
    ### SCHEMA
    Add one JSON-LD WebPage + two ItemList entries for the 4 wall art categories and 4 service categories using URLs above.
    , make the canvas paintings metalposter and ohther h2 navigationable nothing happening when clicked make it work for all
